:INFO
Vintage Mac Parts Sourcing Guide
Where to find logic boards, capacitors, batteries, and replacement parts for compact Macintosh restoration.

:TASK
[ ] Logic board caps: Mouser or Digi-Key, search by value and footprint from service manual
[ ] PRAM battery: search for 1/2 AA 3.6V lithium, Tadiran TL-5902 or equivalent
[ ] Floppy drives: eBay, check seller feedback for tested units
[ ] Analog boards: 68kMLA forums and Marketplace
[ ] Flyback transformers: Uniserver or reclaim from donor Mac
[ ] Keyboard caps and cases: Retro Mac Cast community listings
[ ] SCSI drives or SD-to-SCSI adapters: SCSI2SD or BlueSCSI

:LINK
https://68kmla.org
68kMLA: Vintage Mac Community, Parts, and Technical Help

:NOTE
The 68kMLA forum is the single most valuable resource for compact Mac restoration. Service manuals, schematics, and experienced restorers are all in one place.
